    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly pampered and is ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
