    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe. This example is powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS, delivering a visceral power band up to an 8,000 RPM ceiling. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual and a limited-slip M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance is complete: subframe reinforcement has been professionally executed, and rod bearings have been replaced with high-clearance shells. The chassis remains exceptionally tight with no bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains factory paint thickness and the interior displays zero bolster wear. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
